'''喀什之戰'''1934年[[新疆战争|新疆战争]]中一次军事对抗。[[阿不都拉·布格拉|阿不都拉·布格拉]]和其他突厥独立思想领导人带领[[维吾尔族|维吾尔族]]、[[柯尔克孜族|柯尔克孜族]]泛突厥战士6天内4次攻击喀什的[[马占仓|马占仓]]领导的[[回族|回族]]和信仰伊斯兰教的[[汉族|汉族]]穆斯林士兵。[[和加尼牙孜|和加尼牙孜]]参与战斗，他的哈密维吾尔士兵自阿克苏开到喀什，300英里长途跋涉1月13日到喀什，参加对疏勒县城的围攻，要赶走回族人。回汉士兵击退泛突厥势力，造成对方严重的人员伤亡。<ref>{{cite news|title=REPULSE REBELS AFTER SIX DAYS|author=AP|newspaper=Spokane Daily Chronicle|date=1 February 1934|url=http://news.google.com/newspapers?id=H34SAAAAIBAJ&sjid=7vQDAAAAIBAJ&pg=4906,16349&dq=tungan&hl=en|accessdate=December 12, 2010|archive-date=2018-09-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180915092221/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=H34SAAAAIBAJ&sjid=7vQDAAAAIBAJ&pg=4906,16349&dq=tungan&hl=en|dead-url=no}}</ref>

中央陆军新编第36师[[马福元|马福元]]猛攻[[喀什|喀什]]打击[[东突厥斯坦伊斯兰共和国|东突厥斯坦伊斯兰共和国]]的[[柯尔克孜族|柯尔克孜族]]、[[维吾尔族|维吾尔族]]叛乱者，解救[[马占仓|马占仓]]及其部队。马福元、马占仓击败赶出剩下的突厥士兵。据估计,为报复[[克孜尔大屠杀|克孜尔大屠杀]]2000到8000维吾尔族平民丧生。<ref name="#1"/> 1934年4月,[[马仲英|马仲英]]将军在[[艾提尕尔清真寺|艾提尕尔清真寺]]亲自发表演讲,告诉维吾尔人忠于[[南京|南京]][[国民政府|国民政府]]。<ref>{{cite book|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=GXj4a3gss8wC&pg=PA79&dq=ma+zhongying+idgah&hl=en&ei=zvobTOHaNcH_lgfNm6CIDg&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=1&ved=0CCkQ6AEwAA#v=onepage&q=ma%20zhongying%20idgah&f=false|title=Xinjiang: China's Muslim borderland|author=S. Frederick Starr|year=2004|publisher=M.E. Sharpe|location=|isbn=0-7656-1318-2|page=79|accessdate=2010-06-28|archive-date=2020-10-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201016190527/https://books.google.com/books?id=GXj4a3gss8wC&pg=PA79&dq=ma+zhongying+idgah&hl=en&ei=zvobTOHaNcH_lgfNm6CIDg&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=1&ved=0CCkQ6AEwAA#v=onepage&q=ma%20zhongying%20idgah&f=false|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=8FVsWq31MtMC&pg=PA196&dq=zhang+peiyuan&hl=en&ei=KWghTIS6OoSglAf09LioAQ&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=9&ved=0CEkQ6AEwCA#v=onepage&q=ma%20zhongying%20id%20kah%20mosque%20nanjing&f=false|title=Eurasian crossroads: a history of Xinjiang|author=James A. Millward|year=2007|publisher=Columbia University Press|location=|isbn=0-231-13924-1|page=200|accessdate=2010-06-28|archive-date=2014-10-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141024052938/http://books.google.com/books?id=8FVsWq31MtMC&pg=PA196&dq=zhang+peiyuan&hl=en&ei=KWghTIS6OoSglAf09LioAQ&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=9&ved=0CEkQ6AEwCA#v=onepage&q=ma%20zhongying%20id%20kah%20mosque%20nanjing&f=false|dead-url=no}}</ref>1934年3月在两个独立事件中几个英国公民在领事馆被新36师杀害。<ref>{{cite news |title=TUNGAN RAIDERS MASSACRE 2,000|author=AP|newspaper=The Miami News|date=17 March 1934|url=http://news.google.com/newspapers?id=rlEtAAAAIBAJ&sjid=RNUFAAAAIBAJ&pg=2598,5980247&dq=tungan&hl=en|accessdate=December 12, 2010}}</ref><ref>{{cite